---
title: Honey BBQ Pulled Chicken Sandwiches with Mac 'n' Cheese & Roasted Green Beans
description: Get backyard BBQ vibes any time of year with this Black History Month-inspired meal. Harissa-spiced shredded chicken is tossed with honey BBQ sauce and loaded into toasted brioche buns. Served alongside are roasted green beans and a decadent baked mac ‘n’ cheese with a crunchy, cheesy panko topping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/677d5cc9a90519950138cd87-7c04db72.jpeg
